character: Welcome, traveler, to our very small prototype demo! The expanse of beautiful scenery in front of you is known as the Nondescript Mountains.
character: Traverse the mountains to find new, extremely secret dialogue at the end! Be swift, traveler, for the end of the world is approaching. Meet me beyond the mountains and I will have your solution.
